Definition: the theory that the parts of any whole cannot exist and cannot be understood except in their relation to the whole
Example: holism holds that the whole is greater than the sum of its parts; holistic theory has been applied to ecology and language and mental states
Synonyms: adj, all, holistic, atomism, holistic_theory, theory, the, that, parts, of, any, whole, cannot, exist, and, be, understood, except, in, their, relation, to, holds, is, greater, than, sum, its, has, been, applied, ecology, language, mental, states
Category: noun.cognition
